Rare Special Items.name: ★ Shadow Daggers | Boreal Forest
Rare Special Items.desc: It has been painted using a forest camouflage hydrographic.
Rare Special Items.lore: The woods can be a dangerous place... never travel alone

Rare Special Items.name: ★ Shadow Daggers | Case Hardened
Rare Special Items.desc: It has been color case-hardened through the application of wood charcoal at high temperatures.
Rare Special Items.lore: A little color never hurt anyone

Rare Special Items.name: ★ Shadow Daggers | Safari Mesh
Rare Special Items.desc: It has been spray-painted using mesh fencing and cardboard cutouts as stencils.
Rare Special Items.lore: A predator is a predator, no matter the environment

Rare Special Items.name: ★ Shadow Daggers | Blue Steel
Rare Special Items.lore: This is the malbec of weapon design - Booth, Arms Dealer

Rare Special Items.name: ★ Shadow Daggers | Forest DDPAT
Rare Special Items.desc: It has been painted using a Digital Disruptive Pattern (DDPAT) hydrographic.
Rare Special Items.lore: By the time you're close enough to notice the pixels it's already too late

Rare Special Items.name: ★ Shadow Daggers | Fade
Rare Special Items.desc: It has been painted by airbrushing transparent paints that fade together over a chrome base coat.
Rare Special Items.lore: This isn't just a weapon, it's a conversation piece - Imogen, Arms Dealer In Training

Rare Special Items.name: ★ Shadow Daggers | Slaughter
Rare Special Items.desc: It has been painted in a zebra-stripe pattern with aluminum and chrome paints with various reflectivities, and has then been covered with a tomato red candy coat.
Rare Special Items.lore: Valeria doesn't pay Javier to ask questions... she pays him to pry out answers

Rare Special Items.name: ★ Shadow Daggers | Stained
Rare Special Items.desc: It has been given a forced patina using lemon and mustard dripped onto the surface.
Rare Special Items.lore: If you think it's messy now, wait until you see it under a blacklight

Rare Special Items.name: ★ Shadow Daggers | Scorched
Rare Special Items.desc: It has been spray-painted in a sun-dappled pattern.
Rare Special Items.lore: The Phoenix is not a symbol of destruction... it's a symbol of rebirth - Valeria Jenner, Revolutionary

Rare Special Items.name: ★ Shadow Daggers | Urban Masked
Rare Special Items.desc: It has been spray-painted using a tangle of masking tape as a stencil.
Rare Special Items.lore: True power is demonstrated with subtle application

Rare Special Items.name: ★ Shadow Daggers | Crimson Web
Rare Special Items.desc: It has been painted using a spider web-patterned hydrographic over a red base coat and finished with a semi-gloss topcoat.
Rare Special Items.lore: Be careful where you walk, you never know where the web is spread

Rare Special Items.name: ★ Shadow Daggers | Night
Rare Special Items.desc: It has individual parts spray-painted solid colors in a night ops color scheme.
Rare Special Items.lore: It's the whisper of the wind... it's the bite at your neck

Covert Skins.name: USP-S | Kill Confirmed
Covert Skins.desc: It has been custom painted with the image of a bullet shattering a skull.
Covert Skins.lore: 2 in the chest, 1 in the head

Covert Skins.name: M4A1-S | Golden Coil
Covert Skins.desc: It has been painted with a hydrographic of an attacking snake.
Covert Skins.lore: The viper can strike from anywhere

Classified Skins.name: AK-47 | Frontside Misty
Classified Skins.desc: It has been painted in vibrant arctic colors.
Classified Skins.lore: I like to work in the snow... it always leaves a pretty picture - Javier Alviso, Fist of the Phoenix

Classified Skins.name: SSG 08 | Big Iron
Classified Skins.desc: It has been custom painted with a yellow and orange hydrographic then slightly distressed.
Classified Skins.lore: A win with an asterisk is still a win - Rona Sabri, Rising Star

Classified Skins.name: G3SG1 | Flux
Classified Skins.desc: It has been painted with purple and silver metallic paints.
Classified Skins.lore: A plan is a list of things that don't happen

Restricted Skins.name: P250 | Wingshot
Restricted Skins.desc: It has been custom painted with a vibrant hydrographic.
Restricted Skins.lore: Sometimes a subtle nudge is all it takes to get what you want - Franz Kriegeld, Phoenix Tactician

Restricted Skins.name: M249 | Nebula Crusader
Restricted Skins.desc: It has been custom painted to look like a classic arcade cabinet.
Restricted Skins.lore: You can use it, but you better put up a quarter first

Restricted Skins.name: MP7 | Special Delivery
Restricted Skins.lore: If I do what you want, will you let me go? - The Phoenix and The Storyteller Part 2

Restricted Skins.name: Galil AR | Stone Cold
Restricted Skins.desc: It has been highlighted with metallic blue paint. The stock and magazine bare its designer's mark.
Restricted Skins.lore: Eventually you need to step outside of your mentor's shadow

Mil-Spec Skins.name: Glock-18 | Wraiths
Mil-Spec Skins.desc: It has lost souls custom painted on the slide.
Mil-Spec Skins.lore: First it pierces the shroud, then it pierces the shadow

Mil-Spec Skins.name: MAG-7 | Cobalt Core
Mil-Spec Skins.desc: It has been custom painted with a futuristic graphic design.
Mil-Spec Skins.lore: Keep him safe, Carmen - The Valkyrie and The Paramour Part 1

Mil-Spec Skins.name: Dual Berettas | Dualing Dragons
Mil-Spec Skins.desc: It has dragons laser-etched on the slide and barrel.
Mil-Spec Skins.lore: Marian was always cooler than Sylvia

Mil-Spec Skins.name: XM1014 | Scumbria
Mil-Spec Skins.desc: It has been subtly painted with metallic paints.
Mil-Spec Skins.lore: Let's not be hasty: there may be another way to get Valeria's attention... - A Father's Love Part 3

Mil-Spec Skins.name: FAMAS | Survivor Z
Mil-Spec Skins.desc: It has been stenciled using masking tape then distressed.
Mil-Spec Skins.lore: What's red and white and fires full auto?

Mil-Spec Skins.name: SCAR-20 | Green Marine
Mil-Spec Skins.desc: It has been given a camouflage pattern with metallic paint.
Mil-Spec Skins.lore: Listen up people... Izaki and Cocinero may be AWOL, but our mission remains the same: we're saving Alex Kincaide - Felix Riley, Commanding Officer

Mil-Spec Skins.name: MAC-10 | Rangeen
Mil-Spec Skins.desc: It has been custom painted with an Ancient Egyptian motif.
Mil-Spec Skins.lore: Can you stand against it's wrathful gaze?
